        {
            "title": "乘聯分會：初步數據顯示5月新能源車市場零售按年升30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘聯分會公布5月份初步統計數據，顯示期內新能源車市場零售105.6萬輛，按年升30%，按月亦增14%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-ap_China-Auto.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-ap_China-Auto.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同期全國乘用車市場零售193萬輛，按年增加13%，按年升10%；以此計算，5月份新能源車市場零售滲透率達53.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首5個月合計，新能源車市場零售計達438萬輛，按年升34%。全國乘用車市場首5個月累計零售880.2萬輛，按年升9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986988-%e4%b9%98%e8%81%af%e5%88%86%e6%9c%83%ef%bc%9a%e5%88%9d%e6%ad%a5%e6%95%b8%e6%93%9a%e9%a1%af%e7%a4%ba5%e6%9c%88%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e8%bb%8a%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-ap_china-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 16:55:29",
