        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股尾市飆近全日高位收市   蘋概股及科網股撐市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股尾市突然揚升，接近全日高位收市，蘋概股午後升勢加劇，龍頭科網成升市功臣，中港地產股也向好，航運股捱沽，新消費股高位阻力大。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23906點，升252點或1.07%，今早開市報23828點，升174點或0.74%，上午最高見23911，升257點或1.09%，尾段升幅急收窄，半日報23740點，升86點或0.36%，午後升幅擴大，接近全日高位收市。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"恒基地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基地產官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基地產官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_06181-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_06181-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基地產官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基地產官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_06181-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日收報5319點，升100點或1.93%，今早開報5269點，升50點或0.97%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8684點，升107點或1.26%，今早以8643點開市，升66點或0.78%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報23796，升256點或1.09%，低水111點 ; 科指期貨報5309點，升100點或1.92%，低水11點 ; 國指期貨報8638點，升113點或1.33%，低水47點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市全日成交2220.26億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蘋概股午後進一步攀升，舜宇光學科技(02382)升5.56%，報63.3元，為表現最佳藍籌股；比亞迪電子(00285)升3.02%，報32.4元 ; 瑞聲科技(02018)升5.49%，報38.45元 ;高偉電子(01415)升7.87%，報24元；鴻騰(06088)升13.11%，報2.33元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">2025年蘋果全球開發者大會(WWDC)將於下周二（10日）開幕。據蘋果官網公布的日程，本屆WWDC將於6月10至14日以網上形式舉行。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍頭科網撐市，阿里巴巴(09988)升3.23%，報118.3元; 美團(03690)升2.63%，報144.4元 ; 小米(01810)升1.5%，報54.25元，三股合計貢獻恒指109點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普再促聯儲局減息，中港地產股向好，恒基地產(00012)半日報24.3元，升4.52%，獲納入富時EPRA Nareit全球房地產指數，同系恒基發展(00097)飆12.7%，報0.142元。恒隆地產(00101)報6.41元，升3.39% ; 長實(01113)報32.9元，升2.17%。 </p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒基地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒基地產官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00012-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒基地產官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華潤置地(01109)全日升3.56%，報26.2元，獲大摩升目標價，由33.6元提高至38.8元，重申「增持」評級 ; 中海外(00688)升1.69%，報13.22元 ; 龍湖(00960)升0.94%，報9.69元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新消費股三強老鋪黃金(06181)、蜜雪集團(02097)、泡泡瑪特(09992)創新高後顯著回吐，老鋪黃金(06181)險守900元，收跌90元或9.05%，報904元，最低曾見888.5元，跌105.5元或10.61%，今早突破千元，開報1000元，升0.6%，最高見1015元，升2.11%或21元，隨即大幅下滑，午後全日低，今年6月27日將有1.214億股禁售期滿。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蜜雪集團(02097)見618.5元上市高位，全日收跌7.72%或47.5元，報568元，泡泡瑪特(09992)見252.6元新高，全日收報243元，跌1.22%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_06181-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_06181-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：老鋪黃金官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他消費股午後跌勢加劇，思摩爾(06969)插11.84%，報20.1元。茶百道(02555)挫7.72%，報10.04元；古茗(01364)挫7.97%，報27.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">航運股受壓，東方海外(00316)跌5.94%，報128.3元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 中遠海控(01919)跌1.94%，報13.16元 ; 太平洋航運(02343)降3.06%，造1.9元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986942-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%b0%be%e5%b8%82%e9%a3%86%e8%bf%91%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e8%98%8b%e6%a6%82%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8a",
