            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "普拉達收購意大利皮革公司Rino Mastrotto其中10%股權。",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外電引述普拉達(Prada，股份編號01913)公布，指普拉達已收購意大利皮革公司Rino Mastrotto其中10%股權。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Rino Mastrotto官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/Rino-Mastrotto-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Rino Mastrotto官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/Rino-Mastrotto-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Rino Mastrotto官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布並未披露交易作價，只表示收購是Prada策略的一部分，旨在增強對生產流程的控制。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據協議，普拉達將向Rino Mastrotto轉讓兩家製革廠，包括位於意大利的Conceria Superior和位於法國的Tannerie Limoges。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">普拉達主席Patrizio Bertelli在聲明表示，投資Rino Mastrotto使集團能加強對生產過程中高度戰略性階段的控制。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14986618-%e6%99%ae%e6%8b%89%e9%81%94%e6%94%b6%e8%b3%bc%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%a9%e7%9a%ae%e9%9d%a9%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8rino-mastrotto%e5%85%b6%e4%b8%ad10%e8%82%a1%e6%ac%8a%e3%80%82",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-web_01913-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 15:45:29",
